  "title": "COOK",
  "description": "<p>Roles & Responsibilities</p><p>Job Description & Requirements</p><ul><li>To cook high quality traditional authentic Bangladesh food, speciality in Bangladesh dishes.</li><li>Should have the knowledge about properties and usage of herbs and spices in food preparation, and to cook Bangladesh dishes in a traditional way.</li><li>To ensure that all the dishes are freshly prepared and the food standards are met.</li><li>Plan and arrange ingredients for next day preparation and orders.</li><li>Need to understand the customer requirements, as per order.</li><li>To Introduce new dishes and menus.</li><li>Need to monitor stock rotation procedures are followed as per inventory.</li><li>Experience in all Bangladesh cuisines.</li><li>To maintain quality of food</li><li>A deep understanding of authentic Bangladesh food preparation.</li><li>Capacity to work under pressure during the extremely busy period.</li><li>May have to work overnight (preferably at night shift until late night).</li></ul>",
